{"tid":2509053,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"公社科新書反對「過洋節」 諷迪士尼麥當勞如穿軍服持槍「侵略」","createTime":"2021-04-29T07:36:14.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-29T07:39:24.000Z","uid":19527,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"63d4e458dc541bcabb1684cbbe09e5c59266c562","tid":2509053,"uid":19527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T07:36:14.000Z","msg":"通識科被重新冠名為公民與社會發展科，課時減半，課程大改，將於今年9月新學期中四級開始推行。《蘋果》檢視出版社提供予學校、尚未有售的公社科樣書，內容指中國人慶祝聖誕對傳統造成衝擊，令西方國家軟實力在中國「不斷滲透和擴張」，又以漫畫描繪迪士尼和麥當勞卡通人物穿軍服「侵略」別國文化等。有文化研究學者質疑該書內容單向和偏頗，以中國政府的反西方立場主導，似為「完成任務」而寫。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210429/6ZOLG533PREO7OZICQGEM7EIUI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210429%2F6ZOLG533PREO7OZICQGEM7EIUI%2F&d=4YJm346n2OvV5E02CjQHwdAAr5%2FwdiPol2qeWm%2BM8v8%3D&h=10dca216\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210429%2F6ZOLG533PREO7OZICQGEM7EIUI%2F&h=534d523e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210429/6ZOLG533PREO7OZICQGEM7EIUI/</a><br />\n<br />\n商家佬心諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2d3b61233008eda0a2639b946f02dc00bb9318d","tid":2509053,"uid":267494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T07:39:07.000Z","msg":"不如唔好學英文啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一陣學咁多英文又俾英國滲透"},{"pid":"feed89f4b847596a20bd93649515e0f8e8633c30","tid":2509053,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T07:39:24.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"gold\">敵視你同M記侵略都講得出，明明係你哋自己開門俾人入嚟<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2508628\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2508628</a><br />\n自己掰開大髀騎住個男人，個男人射完就告佢強姦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2508795\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2508795</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/36